{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db8ed5c0af","title":"要将、宋实践在西安所商定之条件致潘汉年电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92ddfeda10","index":0,"year":1937,"month":1,"day":5,"articleId":"db8ed5c0af"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"980a0afb77","type":"paragraph","text":"要将、宋实践在西安所商定之条件","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"db8ed5c0af"},{"id":"2c63f7bc55","type":"paragraph","text":"致潘汉年电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"db8ed5c0af"},{"id":"a69f7497bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年1月5日）汉年同志：恩来在西安与宋子文及蒋介石商定之条件：（一）停战撤兵。（二）初步改组南京政府，三个月复彻底改组。（三）释放政治犯、保证民主权利。（四）停止剩共，联红抗日，划定防地，供给军费，苏区照旧，共党公开。（五）联俄并与英美合作。（六）西北交张学良处理。未子文要我派代表在上海与他接拾，你应速找宋子文弄清南京近日之变化，并要宋子文实践上述诺言","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"db8ed5c0af"},{"id":"ea32ac8f42","type":"paragraph","text":"洛毛五日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"db8ed5c0af"}],"page":{"id":"80bb2b8b9f","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"db8ed5c0af","start":119,"end":119}}}},"__N_SSG":true}